  "body": "**To Reproduce**\r\nSteps to reproduce the behavior:\r\n1. Go to Nethermind Directory\r\n2. Run nethermind with flags --Sync.SnapSync false --Sync.FastSync false --config mainnet\r\n3. Observe: unable to sync - node is unable to finish BeaconHeaders.\r\n\r\nRootcause: it still takes \"Pivot\" into consideration.\r\nWhenever additional flag --Sync.PivotNumber 0 is provided, sync progressing well.\r\nWhenever FastSync=false, we should ignore Pivots.\r\n",
